{
  "stem": "7546.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the funny part of it was that these Jews that came from Germany or from Vienna, some of them were half-Jews, some of them were one-quarter Jews.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And some of them came in with their wives or husbands who were not Jews, but they elected to come with their wife or their husband.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And to get ahead of my story, about a year or two later, if the husband or the wife that was Jewish died, then they were able to make an application to go back to Germany once they had proven that they're of true, Aryan race.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I became very good friend with one fellow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Aaron Vogel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His father was Jewish, his mother was Christian, And the three of them came into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he worked with me in the same commando.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we became very good friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Very good friends.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As time went on, the food was getting worse and worse and harder to get.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The bread was not even the same.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The bread started to get, like, gooey, like plaster, soft plaster in some-- some instances.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It depends what kind of bread you got.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of them didn't bake through, some- some of them was mixed, or some of them was just made heavier, so that whoever was baking the bread didn't watch it, or they couldn't help themselves.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It-- it did get worse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The ration of food that you were getting-- every 10 days-- was smaller.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Many a time, you didn't get-- you only got that brown sugar, but the brown sugar was very soft and moist, like it was never worked out [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
